# Privacy Policy for Mic Streamer

Effective Date: 4/28/2025

Mic Streamer does not collect, store, or share any personal information.

## Data Collection
- The app uses your device’s microphone solely to stream audio locally over your network.
- No audio or data is sent to any external servers or stored.

## Permissions
- The app requests microphone access to function.
- No other device permissions are required.

## Third-Party Services
- Mic Streamer does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services.

## Contact
If you have any questions, contact me at: https://github.com/NeoVectorX

